issue.title: Deep links
issue.body:
Deeplinks support added.
Example of the deeplink:
`
loopr-ios://p2p/Hash=PUTHASHHERE&Ratio=1&Auth=PUTAUTHHERE
`
This could be formed instead of current QR code with JSON in it.
